# Coding Standards

Before editing code, read:

- `ai-framework/standards/coding-rules.md`
- `ai-framework/standards/architecture-rules.md`
- `ai-framework/standards/testing-rules.md`
- Module specs in `.github/specs/` or `ai-framework/modules/coding/specs/` when applicable

General rules:

- Prefer simple, maintainable code
- Avoid unnecessary abstractions
- Keep functions focused
- Preserve existing public APIs unless explicitly instructed
- Handle errors explicitly
- Add tests for behaviour, not implementation details
- Update documentation when behaviour changes

Module path: `Code/{{AREA_NAME}}/{{MODULE_NAME}}/`
